  "title": "(ASAP) Jr Sales & Marketing  ( no experience needed! mentorship provided)",
  "description": "<p><em>(Mentorship Provided | No Experience Needed)</em></p><p>Looking to start a meaningful career with growth potential? Join our team as an <strong>Education Training Sales Advisor</strong>. No prior experience? No problem — we provide full training and 1-on-1 mentorship!<br /></p><p><strong>What You'll Do:</strong><br />- Engage customers and understand their need <br />- Present and recommend suitable products <br />- Build strong customer relationships <br /></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong><br />- Good communication skills <br />- Positive, sales-driven attitude <br />- Team player <br /> </p><p><strong>Benefits: </strong><br />- Training provided <br />- Attractive commisions <br />- Career progression opportunities <br />- Travel opportunities <br /></p><p><strong>Apply now and join us! - lets create memories together!</strong></p>",
